‚úÖ C√°ch 2: X√≥a b·∫±ng .Range(...).Delete d·ª±a tr√™n v·ªã tr√≠ tuy·ªát ƒë·ªëi trong worksheet

Sub DeleteFromFourthRow_Absolute()
    Dim ws As Worksheet
    Dim tbl As ListObject
    Dim startRow As Long
    Dim totalRows As Long

    Set ws = ThisWorkbook.Sheets("Sheet1")
    Set tbl = ws.ListObjects("Table1")

    If Not tbl.DataBodyRange Is Nothing Then
        totalRows = tbl.DataBodyRange.Rows.Count

        If totalRows >= 4 Then
            startRow = tbl.DataBodyRange.Rows(4).Row  ' D√≤ng th·ª±c t·∫ø tr√™n sheet
            totalRows = tbl.DataBodyRange.Rows(totalRows).Row

            ' X√≥a to√†n b·ªô d√≤ng trong worksheet (kh√¥ng ch·ªâ trong b·∫£ng)
            ws.Rows(startRow & ":" & totalRows).Delete
        End If
    End If
End Sub

